\ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5195353  got}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid12397272\charrsid2513566  any connection with Frank's later interest in petite }{\rtlch\fcs1 
