\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5195353 gue, to ensure he could have a l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid12397272\charrsid2513566 
